snippet.title: Jurassic Snap - Trailer Gameplay
snippet.description:
Discover an exoplanet populated by dinosaurs and take cute pictures along your journey!

Complete the Dinopedia and discover everything about this new planet.

The game is coming on PC, PCVR, Quest 2 and PSVR !
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1103660/Jurassic_Snap/

Follow the news of the game on Twitter 👉 https://twitter.com/JurassicSnap
